AUTHORS
=======

Knowledge Constellation Explorer
An interactive tool that turns any topic into an explorable "galaxy" of
connected concept stars. Free, open-source, single-file web app.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Original author & creator
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gurpreet Singh  (@Gurpreet-Singh-offensive-Security)
GitHub:  https://github.com/Gurpreet-Singh-offensive-Security
Project: https://github.com/Gurpreet-Singh-offensive-Security/knowledge-constellation

